i thought i'd do something fun and try pixel art for the first time.

this was a difficult challenge to say the least but it turned out fairly decent imo. i am planning to continue doing pixel art and become better throughout this year.

this is one of many pixel editions that I will be releasing this year. this token will be a burn-to-mint for future releases as well as it'll be a part of my history/journey of growing as an artist.

it's a free mint as I am not the best artist and its a joyous occassion so it should be celebrated.
